description.html:
Cellular Field Tester (Not applied RF and Network Candidate)

Location: Cupertino, CA

Job Description:

1. Expertise on 3GPP specs for 3G/4G/5G technologies

2. Able to operate Android and Apple products (iPhone, Watch, Mac)

3. Experienced Field Testing - inclusive of issue investigation and representation

4. Experience of 3-4 years into Mobile device testing

5. Perform testing and sending daily report to client

6. Log analysis & debugging UE issues.

7. Aware of logging tools like QxDM, QCAT, Wireshark, STT, ELT etc.

Primary Skillsets:

1. 3-4 years of experience in smartphone field testing

2. Excellent understanding of 3GPP specs for 3G/4G/5G technologies

3. Hands on experience of Android and Apple products like smartphones and smart watches.

4. Worked for carrier certification for USA operator (viz. Verizon, AT&T & T-Mobile)

5. Log analysis & debugging UE issues.

Job Type: Full-time

Pay: From $120,000.00 per year

Experience level:

  • 10 years
  • 5 years
  • 6 years
  • 7 years
  • 8 years
  • 9 years

Schedule:

  • 8 hour shift

Ability to commute/relocate:

  • Cupertino, CA: Reliably commute or willing to relocate with an employer-provided relocation package (Required)

Work Location: In person

Location: Cupertino, CA

Job Description:

1. Expertise on 3GPP specs for 3G/4G/5G technologies

2. Able to operate Android and Apple products (iPhone, Watch, Mac)
